<TextBlock Margin="5,5,5,5" ToolTip="{Binding Source={StaticResource Settings}, Path=datFolderPath}" Style="{StaticResource ConfigTextBox}" Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="0" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Text="Hover to view selected dat folder path"/>

<Button ToolTip="Select the game folder (which is in the same directory of where your game exe resides). This is needed because the overlay will read the *unique signatures* of the files within the folder and thus show which files you have used in a quest run" Grid.Row="0" Grid.Column="0" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Content="(Mandatory) Select Game Folder" Click="GameFolderButton_Click"/>
